Instructions to run Biblioteca App
=================================================
1. Run Main

2. Enter a library number and password register into user.xml or add them to this file.

3. Choose the option 1 to set the item type.

4. Choose option 3 to checkout a book or movie (previously you must to choose a type in the option 1).

5. Choose option 4 to return a book or movie (previously you must to choose a type in the option 1).

6 Choose the option 5 to show the user information.

Enjoy the Biblioteca App!
